---
title: Teriyaki Turkey Stir-fry with sugar snaps and bell pepper
description: This teriyaki turkey stir-fry features tender fried peppers and sugar snap peas for beautiful colour and crunch. This is a simple and quick-to-make dish that's not to be missed!
